programme.title: Widuri: Buang Segala Tentang Dia Ep20
programme.desc: Alisa berkahwin dengan Zaid atas pilihan keluarga, namun Zaid meninggalkannya untuk kembali kepada kekasih lamanya, Sue. Ibra, bekas majikan Alisa yang telah lama menyimpan perasaan terhadapnya, berusaha untuk menawan hati Alisa semula. Dalam episod ini, Zaid kerap datang ke kafe Alisa. Zaid ingin memujuk Alisa kembali padanya kerana mahukan duit Alisa untuk membayar hutang along. Ibra memberi amaran pada Zaid supaya jangan mengganggu Alisa. Su isteri Zaid telah tahu yang Zaid kembali mencari Alisa. Pelakon: Dayang Areeda, Syaffiq Sahli, Mustaqim Bahadon, Ily Mokhtar, Jay Iswazir, Azzahra Ahmad, Aishah Azman, Juita Johari, Silfeny Osman, Olan Lam, Ieka Zulkifli, dan Danial Dhasuki.

programme.title: Ronda Roda S3 Ep7
programme.desc: Ronda Roda kali ini, menampilkan kereta Honda WRV, Mira Rizam dan Hazmi. Yang dihoskan oleh Azizul Ammar dengan mempamerkan kereta baru dari Hondadan hasil tangan dari Mira dan Hazmi.

programme.title: Kesempatan Keduda
programme.desc: Cerita berpusat pada Abi (Raffi Ahmad), seorang pekerja korporat yang baru sahaja bercerai dengan isterinya, Maya (Dinda Kanya Dewi), kerana masalah perselingkuhan. Di sisi lain, Ken (Zizan Razak) juga mengalami perceraian dengan isterinya, Baby (Nagita Slavina). Selepas persidangan perceraian, Abi dan Ken bertemu di sebuah warung kopi dan mula berkongsi cerita tentang kehidupan mereka. Mereka berdua merasa bahawa perceraian adalah titik terendah dalam hidup mereka, tetapi pemilik warung kopi memberi mereka perspektif baru bahawa menjadi duda bukanlah akhir segalanya.

programme.title: Jamu Nesan S1 Ep15
programme.desc: Sofi beri bukti bukan Fendy yang tembak Tok Chai, dia telah diperangkap. Madam Zoora diselubungi perasaan bersalah dan menyesal kerana nesankan Fendy. Madam Zoora kini kehilangan orang yang paling disayanginya dan juga mungkin akan kehilangan Tok Chai kerana keadaan Tok Chai semakin kritikal. Tok Chai langsung tidak respon dan mungkin harapan untuk hidup terlalu tipis. Madam Zoora makin hari makin tidak dapat tumpukan pada perniagaannya dan Big Bro makin risau dengan sikap Madam Zoora.

programme.title: Dapur Bujang S16 Ep6

programme.title: Jendela Hati Ep14
programme.desc: Sepanjang berada di UK, Farah diasak rindu terhadap Lukman dan Zahin. Dia sibukkan diri dengan studi demi melupakan segala kemelut yang melanda di samping menjaga kandungannya yang makin membesar. Farah tidak tahu bahawa Lukman ditahan di lokap. Berita kematian Mama akibat heart attack bukan sahaja merentap jiwanya, malah meragut seluruh kebahagiaan keluarga. Lukman dihambat penyesalan tak berkesudahan. Zulkarnain ikat jamin dan menyelesaikan segala tuntutan syarikat untuk membebaskan Lukman. Liza dan Nazim seumpama tulang belakang yang sentiasa menyokong Farah di Manchester. Farah terkejut apabila Lukman tiba-tiba muncul di depan pintu apartment untuk memohon maaf kepadanya. Farah tidak sanggup berdepan dengan Lukman hingga menyebabkan mereka bertengkar. Tanpa sengaja, Farah tergelincir dan terjatuh di tangga hingga mengalami pendarahan

programme.title: Dihatiku Ada Kamu Ep25
programme.desc: Rian tanya kenapa Adif dan Afeeq datang ke butiknya. Afeeq risau, Rian marah sebab sibuk nak tahu hal dia. Adif juga tak suka cara Rian, lalu bawa Rian pulang. Adif, tanya tentang siapa Indri. Rian dan Adif bergaduh . Afeeq tanya Indri tentang hubungan dengan Rian. Indri kata dia tak ganggu isteri orang, tapi Afeeq tetap beri amaran. Rian beritahu Adif dia nak ke Vietnam urusan kerja. Rian tak mahu jumpa Adif lagi sebab dia dah penat nak layan semua kerenah dan cemburu Adif. Tarikh dua bulan sudah hampir dan ia buatkan Adif susah hati sebab Rian sudah menjauhinya semula. Fitrin tunggu Adif, ugut akan ganggu keluarga jika Adif tak jumpa dia. Adif marah, cekak leher Fitrin. Faisal datang, Adif lepaskan Fitrin dan pergi. Adif memandu laju ke sekolah Farhan, risau sesuatu berlaku. Dia terlanggar tembok selepas mengelak kereta lain. Adif cedera, Rian terkejut dan apabila Rian pulang ke Malaysia, Farhan sudah ikut Adif dan Adif mahu ambil Farhan. Rian mengaku dia salah sangka dan tuduh Adif macam macam. Mereka bergaduh besar sehingga Adif hampir melafazkan cerai tapi Rian cuba merayu.

programme.title: Dihatiku Ada Kamu Ep26
programme.desc: Rian pengsan dan bila sedar dia sudah berada di rumah baru Adif. Adif jaga Rian dengan baik dan Farhan sudah pun Idris dan Rania bawa pulang dahulu. Rian bersyukur Adif tidak menceraikannya. Hubungan mereka Kembali baik dan Rian sedari keikhlasan Adif tapi berlaku salah faham pula apabila Rian dengar perbualan telefon Adif dengan seseorang. Rian sangka Adif nak perangkap dia saja. Rian larikan diri. Adif cuba terangkan sekali lagi sehingga kali ini Adif sudah putus asa sebab Rian masih tak percayakannya. Adif beri syarat jika Rian pergi, akan jatuh satu talak. Dan Rian pergi dengan rasa amat sedih. Idris beritahu, Rian dan Adif salah faham. idris percaya Adif lebih daripada Rian. Adif datang. Adif terangkan. apa yang Rian dengar malam tadi adalah untuk stalker iaitu Fitrin, bukan Rian. Adif jelaskan tentang manipulasi Fitrin. Fitrin datang serang mereka tanpa mereka jangka sehingga tertikam Adif semasa Adif nak selamatkan Rian. Afeeq juga sedar Fitrin telah pergunakan dia juga. Fitrin dapat ditangkap. Hujung kisah proses rujuk semula antara Rian dan Adif setelah masing masing tidak dapat hidup sendiri dan dihat mereka masih ada cinta antara sesama mereka.

programme.title: Anggun Mikayla Ep12
programme.desc: Perjalanan hidup Mikayla sentiasa bersimpang-siur dengan dugaan sejak dia mencelikkan mata birunya ke dunia. Status kelahirannya membuatkan dia seringkali menerima cacian penduduk kampung dan menjadi mangsa buli semasa kecil. Mekap adalah cara Mikayla menidakkan kewujudannya sendiri. Dia berselindung di sebalik rambut palsu hitam untuk menyorokkan rambut auburnnya serta mengenakan pelbagai jenis mekap untuk menggelapkan warna kulit kerana keinginannya untuk tampak Melayu. Siang, Mikayla bekerja sebagai jurumekap artis dan apabila malam tiba, dia menjelma sebagai pontianak. Pertemuan Mikayla dengan Idriz dalam satu insiden lucu telah mencipta satu hubungan aneh yang tidak bernama. Dalam diam, Idriz menyimpan rasa tetapi keinginannya terbatas kerana tanggungjawabnya pada keluarga. Jurugambar yang bekerja bersamanya, Asif yang suka mengusik Mikayla mulai tersedar yang usikannya sudah bertukar menjadi perasaan sebenar. Tetapi, dia terlajak memikat pelakon popular bernama Andria, sebelum tersedar tentang perasaannya terhadap Mikayla. Sedang Mikayla dalam keadaan celaru, lelaki dari masa silamnya, Aidan pula muncul kembali, menagih kemaafan kerana meninggalkan parut panjang di dahinya. Aidan yang kini sudah bergelar pelakon popular cuba memadamkan kenangan sakit mereka demi merebut hati yang dirinduinya itu. Tetapi, impian Mikayla hanya satu, berhadapan dengan masa silamnya dan mencantas kebencian mama. Cinta bukan destinasi yang diimpi. Namun, hatinya terus menjadi buruan oleh tiga orang lelaki.

programme.title: Dihatiku Ada Kamu Ep13
programme.desc: Adif selamatkan Rian yang hampir dilanggar basikal. Di rumah, Rian bersiap untuk pergi, tetapi tidak menemukan kunci dan marah. Adif menghantar bunga putih dan kad ke rumah, tapi Rian terkejut dan segera keluar untuk bertemu Mun dan rakan-rakan yang berusaha lari dari pengintip yang Adif upah untuk bawa Rian ke lapangan terbang. Rian bertemu mama papa dan Afeeq untuk sama sama terbang ke Sydney. Apabila Adif dapat tahu, dia panik mencari Rian di KLIA, tetapi Rian sudah berada di pintu keberangkatan. Mereka terpisah juga walaupun Adif amat sedih tapi tak dapat halang Rian pergi. Rian tinggalkan surat akhir buat Adif tanda dia masih sayang tetapi dia perlu berada jauh daripada Adif demi keselamatan keluarganya dan anak yang akan lahir nanti.

programme.title: Ong Bak 2
programme.desc: Berlatarkan Thailand abad ke-15, filem ini berkisarkan Tien, anak kepada seorang bangsawan yang dibunuh. Ditawan dan dijual sebagai hamba, Tien diselamatkan daripada kematian oleh Chernang, ketua Pha Beek Khrut, sekumpulan artis mempertahankan diri yang pakar dalam pelbagai gaya tempur Asia.

programme.title: Two Sisters
programme.desc: Selepas seorang gadis dibebaskan dari rumah sakit jiwa, dia disatukan semula dengan kakaknya dan mereka kembali ke rumah keluarga yang ditinggalkan. Namun, kedua-dua beradik itu menyimpan rahsia gelap dan tragis keluarga yang mula terungkap selepas kepulangan mereka.

programme.title: Bini-bini Ku Gangster
programme.desc: Manja dan Herry adalah sepasang suami isteri yang sangat romantik dan saling sayang menyayangi. Tanpa disedari oleh Herry, Manja adalah ketua kumpulan kepada sebuah geng gengster di Kuala Lumpur. Di pejabat,Herry kerap dibuli Mat Saja termasuk menyuruh Herry menggantikan tempatnya semasa ulangtahun perkahwinan Manja dan Herry yang ke2. Manja bengang lalu menghantar orang-orangnya memukul Mat Saja.

programme.title: Ong Bak 3
programme.desc: Kisah pahlawan Tien, yang telah ditangkap oleh panglima perang yang kejam Tuan Rajasena. Tien melarikan diri daripada cengkaman Rajasena, pulih daripada kecederaannya yang melumpuhkan dengan bantuan Guru Bua, dan kembali untuk berhadapan dengan Bhuti Sangkha, yang telah menggantikan Rajasena sebagai penjahat utama.

programme.title: Black S1 Ep5
programme.desc: Seorang pembunuh upahan sedang menjejakinya lalu Black menyedari masanya dalam badan Malik semakin suntuk. Dia mesti menamatkan misinya dengan cepat dan satu-satunya harapan yang dia ada adalah menyakinkan Sofia untuk membantunya. Dia terjumpa sebuah bilik rahsia di dalam rumah Malik di mana tersimpan barang-barang yang jelas sekali disorok oleh Malik. Sementara itu, Sofia nampak satu pembunuhan bakal berlaku yang mengganggu perasaannya sehingga merangsang dia untuk bertindak. Dia memujuk Black untuk pulang ke kampung halaman mereka di Seri Setia untuk menyiasat kes itu. Anehnya, penyiasatan Borhan ke atas kes Nurul Najwa juga membawanya ke Seri Setia. Di sana, dia ketemu semula rakan sekerja lamanya, yang menyimpan rahsia tentang kes dingin yang berlaku 20 tahun lalu.

programme.title: Din Tiger Ep3
programme.desc: Din Tiger berusaha mencari kebenaran di sebalik kematian isterinya, tetapi keadaan bertambah rumit akibat penyelewengan yang dilakukan oleh Anat terbongkar.

programme.title: Din Tiger Ep4
programme.desc: Ketegangan meningkat di majlis hari jadi Elyn apabila Din dihina dan dihalau, mengakibatkan konflik yang berterusan berlaku antara ayah dan anak.

programme.title: Plan B Ep7
programme.desc: Mengisahkan setelah Que bebas dari tahanan polis, dia menasihati Khai dan Cika tidak meneruskan niat mereka untuk mengadakan lumba kereta secara haram, kerana polis sedang menjejaki aktiviti mereka. Khai pula berdepan dengan masalah kewangan, kerana ayahnya telah memberhentikan pemberian wang poket kepadanya dan dia juga banyak berhutang dengan Cika, membuatkan Khai seringkali bertelagah dan bersikap kasar dengan ayahnya. Que ingin membantu mententeramkan jiwa Khai, walaupun ibunya, menegah Que bercampur gaul dengan Khai dan lain-lain, tetapi Que terpaksa membantu Khai dengan alasan bahawa mereka sekeluarga telah terhutang budi dengan keluarga Khai.

programme.title: Cinderella's Curse
programme.desc: Cinderella, dalam keadaan terdesak, memanggil ibu pari-parinya melalui sebuah kitab kuno yang terikat dengan kulit manusia, dengan harapan untuk menuntut keadilan dan membalas dendam terhadap ibu tiri dan kakak tirinya yang sentiasa menyeksa serta menindasnya tanpa henti.

programme.title: Araf 5
programme.desc: Mengisahkan tentang seorang wanita muda yang mendapati dirinya dalam mimpi ngeri yang mengerikan ketika cuba menyara keluarga bekas teman lelakinya yang membunuhnya. Zeynep, seorang wanita muda, kecewa apabila dia mengetahui bahawa bekas teman lelakinya Kadir membunuhnya dengan cara digantung. Mengucapkan takziah kepada keluarga Kadir, Zeynep memutuskan untuk tinggal bersama mereka selama beberapa hari untuk menyara mereka atas desakan ibu Kadir. Bagaimanapun, tiada apa yang dilihat di dalam rumah itu menggambarkan kebenaran. Dalam proses ini, Zeynep mengetahui tentang kematian Kadir daripada entiti yang menghantui rumah itu. Diseret ke dalam pusaran, Zeynep mendapati dirinya di tengah-tengah Api Penyucian, tempat antara dua alam.

programme.title: Ong Bak 2
programme.desc: Berlatarkan Thailand abad ke-15, filem ini berkisarkan Tien, anak kepada seorang bangsawan yang dibunuh. Ditawan dan dijual sebagai hamba, Tien diselamatkan daripada kematian oleh Chernang, ketua Pha Beek Khrut, sekumpulan artis mempertahankan diri yang pakar dalam pelbagai gaya tempur Asia.

programme.title: Karantina
programme.desc: 5 pelajar pergi ke lawatan sekolah di Pulau Karantina untuk kelas Sejarah. Tetapi salah seorang daripada mereka akan tersesat ke hospital terbiar dan rakan sekelasnya perlu mencarinya, menghadapi ancaman paranormal di sepanjang jalan.

programme.title: Abang Long Fadil 2
programme.desc: Kisah mengenai Fadil yang terjerumus ke dalam dunia mafia yang diketuai oleh Taji Samprit dan anaknya, Wak Doyok. Satu insiden menyebabkan Inspektor Wahab dan Inspektor Shuib mengesyaki Fadil sebagai Tiger, seorang pembunuh upahan profesional.

programme.title: Two Sisters
programme.desc: Selepas seorang gadis dibebaskan dari rumah sakit jiwa, dia disatukan semula dengan kakaknya dan mereka kembali ke rumah keluarga yang ditinggalkan. Namun, kedua-dua beradik itu menyimpan rahsia gelap dan tragis keluarga yang mula terungkap selepas kepulangan mereka.

programme.title: Din Tiger Ep4
programme.desc: Ketegangan meningkat di majlis hari jadi Elyn apabila Din dihina dan dihalau, mengakibatkan konflik yang berterusan berlaku antara ayah dan anak.

programme.title: Awoken
programme.desc: Apabila tiada apa yang boleh dilakukan untuk pesakit Insomnia Fatal Familial di hospital, seorang pelajar perubatan telah menyuruh abangnya dipindahkan ke kemudahan rahsia di ruang bawah tanah untuk rawatan alternatif.

programme.title: Kapsul
programme.desc: Kapsul masa wawasan 2020 yang ditanam oleh Tun Dr. Mahathir Mohamad telah dicuri dan membawa Zohri kembali ke masa lalu. Zohri kini terperangkap di tengah-tengah pergolakan bangsa Melayu untuk mencapai kemerdekaan dan membawa bangsa Melayu keluar dari belenggu kemiskinan. Zohri melihat dan merasai sendiri erti perjuangan umatnya yang tidak pernah dibayangkannya selama ini. Dia lihat, dia rasa dan kini dia mula faham betapa peritnya liku-liku sejarah negara dan bangsa. Perjalanan Zohri berterusan dari satu zaman ke satu zaman dan tiada siapa yang dapat mengembalikannya ke zamannya melainkan dirinya sendiri.

programme.title: Fobia Malam Pertama
programme.desc: Fobia Malam Pertama menceritakan tentang Zaty, pelajar sebuah kolej tempatan di Pulau Pinang yang fobia untuk bercinta.

programme.title: Plan B Ep11
programme.desc: Mengisahkan Mika, Khai dan Iris dikejar polis. Mereka berjaya menyembunyikan diri dalam salah sebuah kedai motorsikal dan menawan seluruh pekerja kedai itu. Dalam keadaan cedera parah ditembak, Mika mengarahkan Khai memeriksa beg yang dirompak mereka. Setelah membukanya, Khai mendapati beg itu mengandungi bungkusan coklat yang dibalut dengan kertas warna keemasan. Kemudian pasukan polis berjaya mengempung lokasi persembunyian mereka. Que yang turut ditahan polis, dibawa bersama untuk memujuk kawan-kawannya menyerah diri.

programme.title: Din Tiger Ep4
programme.desc: Ketegangan meningkat di majlis hari jadi Elyn apabila Din dihina dan dihalau, mengakibatkan konflik yang berterusan berlaku antara ayah dan anak.

programme.title: Barajiwa Ep5
programme.desc: Ashikin membantu Uzair melarikan diri daripada Imran tetapi menerima akibatnya. Uzair tertarik dengan Noramina. Imran kecewa kerana Madi belum sedar daripada koma. Janice berputus asa dengan Ashikin. Perlawanan yang telah diatur dari mula, Uzair kalah dalam perlawanan timbal balik kepada Hatta. Imran perlu berunding tentang perebutan kawasan dengan seorang lelaki misteri bernama Along.

programme.title: Pelepas Saka
programme.desc: Sejak pulang ke kampung, Alisya sering diganggu dengan bayangan seorang wanita tua dan kadang-kala dia akan mendengar bunyi buaian yang berayun di luar rumah. Alisya juga sering diganggu dengan mimpi yang bukan-bukan menyebabkan dia terfikir-fikir apa yang sedang terjadi padanya. Suatu malam, usai saja majlis doa selamat di rumah Adnan, Asiah telah melakukan upacara melepaskan sakanya pada Haider. Setelah melepaskan sakanya, wajah Asiah berubah menjadi sangat tua dan badannya membongkok. Asiah hilang jejak selepas itu. Haider tidak menyedari bahawa dirinya kini didampingi oleh saka Asiah dan perangainya mula berubah. Dia menjadi panas-baran, suka makan telur mentah, sentiasa panas dan mula mengsyaki hubungan antara Raden dan Alisya. Raden juga diganggu oleh saka Asiah dengan menjelmakan diri sebagai Alisya. Raden mula tidak sedap hati dan memberitahu hal ini pada Adnan. Raden juga berusaha mencari punca setiap gangguan yang berlaku di rumah tersebut sehingga membawanya ke rumah Asiah. Di situ barulah Raden tahu tentang kisah yang terjadi.

programme.title: Superbike
programme.desc: Ia berkisar tentang kehidupan seharian sekumpulan penunggang motosikal superbike yang menggelar kumpulan mereka sebagai 'Pirate Bikers' dan diketuai oleh Bugs (Kamal Adli). Berlumba-lumba di jalanan, kejar-mengejar, berkonvoi dan disaman oleh polis telah menjadi rasa masam dalam kehidupan mereka yang berkongsi minat yang sama.

programme.desc: Rachel dan Anna pulang ke rumah dua tahun selepas kematian ibu mereka, dan dapati bandar itu ditinggalkan dengan rumah mereka dalam keadaan kacau dan kotor. Apabila Rachel mula mengalami halusinasi mengenai ibu mereka yang sudah meninggal dan sesuatu artifak purba, petunjuk-petunjuk menakutkan mula terbongkar mengenai masa lalu keluarga mereka.

programme.title: Gemersik Berbisik Ep4
programme.desc: Seorang kanak-kanak mempunyai rahsia misteri belajar tarian Ulek Mayang. Dia dipengaruhi oleh arwah ibu dan kakak-kakaknya yang meninggal dunia di laut.

programme.title: Sebelum Titik Noktah Ep3
programme.desc: Hariz mulai punyai suspek baru iaitu Budi yang sebelum ini hanya baik dan dilihat sebagai peminat setianya. Namun Hariz dapat tahu di rumah Budi ada seorang lelaki tua diikat kaki tangannya. Siapa lelaki ini?

programme.title: Sebelum Titik Noktah Ep4
programme.desc: Hariz yakin Budi ada kena mengena kerana Budi ada masa dia bertengkar dengan Andy, Hariz tahu Budi adalah peminatnya, mungkin peminat ini bunuh mereka yang cuba sakiti Hariz.

programme.title: Sebelum Titik Noktah Ep5
programme.desc: Hariz terpaksa dibebaskan semula, dan saat inilah Hariz mahu larikan dirinya, dia kembali ke kabin yang mana dia lihat sudah berubah kedudukan, dia yakin pembunuh masih ada di situ. Banyak rahsia disimpan sang penulis novel ini kian dirungkai.

programme.title: Sebelum Titik Noktah Ep6
programme.desc: Haridz dikunjungi seorang lelaki misteri. Ganesh tidak tahu tentang kejadian ini, dia sendiri fikir kes ini sudah habis, namun kemudiannya mayat Pokwe ditemui di kawasan kampung.

programme.title: Barajiwa Ep6
programme.desc: Noramina kagum dengan kemahiran bertarung Uzair dan menawar pekerjaan sebagai pengawal peribadinya. Uzair kini mempunyai pekerjaan yang sesuai dan boleh menyewa tempat tinggal sendiri. Hatta mula sedar ada sesuatu yang baik dan istimewa pada Uzair. Uzair mula mesra dengan Noramina.

programme.title: Bodyguard
programme.desc: Seorang lelaki yang kehilangan cinta dan keinginannya untuk hidup bekerja bersama rakan-rakan zaman kanak-kanaknya di sebuah syarikat pinjaman persendirian. Suatu hari, dia bertemu dengan seorang wanita yang sedang dikejar oleh penyerang yang tidak dikenali. Wanita itu merupakan satu-satunya pewaris kepada sebuah korporat. Dia sedang diburu oleh seseorang yang cuba merampas syarikat tersebut. Sementara itu, pemilik syarikat pinjaman tersebut mula mencari wanita itu.

programme.title: Kau,Aku Dan Dia
programme.desc: Mengisahkan Nancy dan Syafiq yang baru tamat pengajian di universiti. Walaupun berlainan bangsa, namun mereka saling mencintai antara satu sama lain. Konflik mula berlaku apabila orang tua ingin menjodohkan mereka dengan orang lain. Syafiq kemudiannya bertemu dengan seorang gadis buta bernama Mastura yang dilanggarnya secara tidak sengaja. Semakin hari, hubungan antara Syafiq dan Mastura menjadi semakin rapat sehingga Nancy berasa tersisih.

programme.title: Bujang Selamat
programme.desc: Sering diganggu budak-budak di kampung, Bujang mula mempelajari ilmu persilatan. Bujang pergi mendaftarkan diri untuk bertanding di satu pertandingan silat namun telah diperli budak-budak lain. Rasa terhina, Bujang pun pergi bertemu seorang guru silat. Bersama guru itu, Bujang mempelajari teknik bersilat yang sangat hebat.

programme.title: Jiran
programme.desc: Mengisahkan Ramlan sekeluarga yang baru berpindah di sebuah kawasan perumahan. Namun, Ramlan melarang isteri dan anaknya Tina daripada bergaul dengan jiran-jiran mereka di situ. Ramlan sendiri beranggapan bahawa dengan berlaku sombong terhadap orang, dirinya akan dipandang mulia. Kesombongan Ramlan itu akhirnya menyusahkan dirinya sendiri apabila berlaku satu insiden yang melibatkan kehilangan Tina.

programme.title: Azura
programme.desc: Seorang jejaka yang berasal daripada keluarga orang berada ingin mengahwini wanita pilihannya, Azura namun ditentang ibu bapanya. Zack mengahwini Azura dan bekerja sebagai buruh untuk menyara keluarganya - ini setelah kewangannya dipotong oleh keluarga. Azura hamil namun dia mula mengesyaki bahawa bayi tersebut bukan miliknya.

programme.title: Bila Jodoh
programme.desc: Mengisahkan seorang lelaki bernama Hasrul yang selalu gagal mencari jodoh untuk dirinya. Dengan secara tidak sengaja, dia sering bertemu Liza namun mereka sering bertikam lidah. Dalam masa yang sama, keluarga Hasrul mencari calon untuk dijodohkan dengannya. Tanpa disedari Hasrul, gadis yang ingin dikenalkan kepadanya ialah Liza.

programme.title: XX Ray
programme.desc: Obsesinya terhadap angkasa lepas telah membuatkan Amir untuk mencipta sebuah topi keledar. Topi keledar ini merupakan penemuan baru apabila ia menggunakan kuasa tahi bintang. Sesiapa sahaja yang memakainya boleh melihat menembusi apa sahaja yang mereka inginkan. Kekacauan berlaku apabila topi itu telah menyebabkan Amir bertukar menjadi halimunan.

programme.title: Tembus
programme.desc: Mengisahkan seorang lelaki bernama Hari yang memegang tanggungjawab besar dalam mengotakan janji agar kehidupan rumahtangganya menjadi semakin baik. Di mata masyarakat, Hari dan isterinya, Izza dianggap sebagai pasangan ideal yang sukses dalam hal rumahtangga dan kerjaya. Namun mereka diuji dengan kehilangan anak dan pelbagai rahsia terbongkar akibat terjadinya peristiwa itu.

programme.title: Cinta Bollywood
programme.desc: Mengisahkan Shahrul, anak Tok Penghulu merangkap seorang penganggur yang tinggal di Parit Buntar bersama keluarganya. Dia menaruh hati kepada seorang gadis bernama Asha. Pada suatu hari, seorang penerbit filem telah datang ke kampungnya untuk membuat penggambaran drama berjudul Cinta Bollywood. Shahrul kemudiannya dilantik menjadi production manager dan pelakon untuk penggambaran drama itu. Ketika penggambaran dibuat, Salman, hero drama itu semakin rapat dengan Asha dan hal ini membuatkan Shahrul cemburu.

programme.title: Cikgu Romantik
programme.desc: Bercita-cita ingin menjadi selebriti terkenal, Azizah mendapat surat uji bakat yang bertempat di Kuala Lumpur. Dia pun pergi dan menetap di rumah temannya, Tila lalu berkenalan bersama seorang guru vokal iaitu Ramli. Muncul pula Shahrul yang mengatakan bahawa raut wajah Azizah seiras dengan isterinya yang telah meninggal dunia.

programme.title: Kasih Farra
programme.desc: Mengisahkan Farra yang bercinta dengan Lokman, seorang lelaki yang jauh lebih tua daripada usianya. Lokman baru pulang ke Malaysia selepas lebih 20 tahun merantau ke luar negara. Tanpa pengetahuan Lokman, Farra ialah anak kepada bekas kekasihnya, Zura. Dalam masa yang sama, Zura sedang mencari Lokman untuk meminta maaf atas apa yang berlaku kepada hubungan mereka di masa lampau.

programme.title: Ali Setan
programme.desc: Ali pelajar universiti yang nakal dan suka bergurau berjumpa Asmidar ketika dalam perjalanan ke universiti. Ali selalu mencari jalan untuk mengusik Asmidar, lama kelamaan perasaan cinta mula berputik antara mereka berdua. Konflik mula terjadi apabila Ali sebenarnya sudah berkahwin dengan Tipah namun atas sebab terpaksa.

programme.title: Nylea & Harris
programme.desc: Mengisahkan Harris yang terpaksa bekerja sebagai pelayan walaupun dia memiliki kelulusan tinggi. Dia kemudiannya berjaya mendapat kerja sebagai arkitek di sebuah firma milik Tan Sri Kadir. Tugas pertama Harris ialah untuk menyiapkan sebuah rumah untuk anak perempuan Tan Sri Kadir iaitu Nylea. Pada mulanya Harris dan Nylea sering bertengkar namun lama kelamaan timbul bibit-bibit percintaan antara mereka berdua. Walau bagaimanapun, muncul pula Chris, bekas tunangan Nylea ke dalam hidup mereka yang membuatkan Harris sangat kecewa.

programme.title: Ali Setan 2
programme.desc: Ikatan yang ingin tercipta terpaksa dileraikan kerana campur tangan keluarga menyebabkan Ali dan Asmidar pergi membawa haluan sendiri. Rancangan untuk mendirikan rumahtangga telah diganggu oleh Jeff yang inginkan Asmidar. Ayah Asmidar pula menyuruhnya berkahwin bersama Jeff - namun setelah beberapa bulan mereka pun bercerai kerana tidak bahagia. Ali dan Asmidar pun bersatu semula.

programme.title: Cinta U-Turn
programme.desc: Mengisahkan Faiz, seorang anak lelaki kepada ahli perniagaan bernama Datuk Shuib yang ingin dijodohkan dengan Juliana. Kekeliruan mula berlaku apabila gambar Juliana telah bertukar dengan gambar orang lain yang tidak menepati citrasa Faiz. Dia melarikan diri dan berkenalan dengan Hafiz. Mereka bersama-sama bekerja di sebuah bengkel. Pada suatu hari, Juliana datang ke bengkel itu dan telah membuatkan Faiz jatuh cinta padanya. Keadaan menjadi huru hara apabila berlakunya penyamaran antara Faiz dan Hafiz dalam memenangi hati bapa Juliana, iaitu Datuk Jamal.

programme.title: Puteri Impian
programme.desc: Pekerja kilang, Puteri Nora sentiasa mengimpikan untuk menjadi seorang puteri raja. Impiannya menjadi kenyataan apabila dia diterima menyertai pertandingan "Memburu Impian". Kehidupannya berubah sekelip mata apabila bertemu Tengku Faizal, seorang putera raja. Namun, Zul, jurukameranya dalam rancangan itu turut menyukai Puteri Nora. Pilihan harus dibuat antara kemewahan atau kebebasan.

programme.desc: Program temu bual santai bersama peminat dan penggiat filem tempatan yang mengupas pengalaman peribadi tetamu berkaitan filem universe Rock arahan Mamat Khalid

programme.title: Bila Dah Sayang
programme.desc: Mengisahkan Kamarudin yang tak jadi bertunang dengan Tengku Suraya kerana kekasihnya itu masih belum bersedia untuk berkahwin. Dalam hati mereka masih ada perasaan sayang antara satu sama lain walaupun mereka sering bertengkar. Namun berlaku satu insiden yang membuatkan Kamarudin terpikat dengan seorang gadis Cina bernama Miss Yap.

programme.title: Puteri Impian 2
programme.desc: Gadis kilang yang menolak lamaran seorang kerabat diraja Tengku Faizal, menaruh hati terhadap jurukamera stesen televisyen, Zul. Nora menyukai Zul tetapi dia telah pun menjalin hubungan bersama Lisa. Adik kepada Tengku Faizal, Tengku Farid ingin membawa semula Nora kembali ke abangnya. Tekad, dia ingin mengangkat semula maruah abangnya.

programme.title: Ali Setan

programme.title: Cinta Bollywood
programme.desc: Mengisahkan Shahrul, anak Tok Penghulu merangkap seorang penganggur yang tinggal di Parit Buntar bersama keluarganya. Dia menaruh hati kepada seorang gadis bernama Asha. Pada suatu hari, seorang penerbit filem telah datang ke kampungnya untuk membuat penggambaran drama berjudul Cinta Bollywood. Shahrul kemudiannya dilantik menjadi production manager dan pelakon untuk penggambaran drama itu. Ketika penggambaran dibuat, Salman, hero drama itu semakin rapat dengan Asha dan hal ini membuatkan Shahrul cemburu.

programme.title: Ali Setan 2

Ayah Asmidar pula menyuruhnya berkahwin bersama Jeff - namun setelah beberapa bulan mereka pun bercerai kerana tidak bahagia. Ali dan Asmidar pun bersatu semula.

Tanpa pengetahuan Lokman, Farra ialah anak kepada bekas kekasihnya, Zura. programme.desc: Three generations of the Jin family live under one roof. Mrs. Jin-Ke mei-man has two sons, You-Tsai and You-De. You-Tsai abandoned the family many years ago, leaving his wife Siou-Ying to shoulder the huge responsibility of the Jin family business selling fish products at market. Although Siou-Ying was betrayed by You-Tsai, she has still been a dutiful daughter to her mother-in-law, and has single-mindedly raised four children.

When Feng-Yi suddenly disappears, the sisters realize they've neglected their mother, who has always supported them. Now they must find her and get their lives back on track.

programme.title: Show Biz (M) Ep1009
programme.desc: Every second counts in "Show Biz" to bring you with the most High Speed star news, exciting live shows and performers interviews.

programme.title: The Borderless World (M) Ep758
programme.desc: Journalist with an infallible nose for a story is leading the audience to explore the world. Exploring how people from different cultures overcome the challenges with collective wisdom.

programme.title: Mr.Player (M) Ep532
programme.desc: Depending on the locations of the missions, Jacky Wu, the leader of the home team, invites various celebrities to take on challenges and bring you excitement every week.

programme.title: Gung Hay Fat Choy (M) Ep36
programme.desc: In a bad economy, many people dream of becoming rich overnight, especially the Jiang family. Mother Jiang pushes her three children to earn money so that they can one day live in luxury. Even her daughter-in-law wishes for the same thing. She hopes that one day she can visit her parents with the money that spills out of her purse.

programme.title: Shock Wave 2
programme.desc: A series of bomb explosions is causing fear in Hong Kong. Former bomb specialist Feng is found in coma at the crime scene and becomes a suspect. To prove his innocence, he seeks help from his former partner Wen. However, it seems revealing the truth is as risky as disposing a bomb

programme.title: Kung Fu Hustle
programme.desc: Mobster Sing aspires to join the Axe Gang. As he stumbles into a slum ruled by eccentric landlords that are kung fu masters in disguise, his actions cause the gang and the landlords to engage in an explosive kung fu battle

programme.title: I Love Hong Kong
programme.desc: Ng Shun and his family return to the public housing estate where he grew up, not to visit his aging father, but to seek refuge after his business has failed. When his family of five squeeze into the small estate unit, Ng Shun is forced to face his long-neglected family problems...

programme.title: Kung Fu Mahjong 3
programme.desc: Gambling tycoon Man suddenly marries his new partner Sophie, which shocked his only son, Ken. In the wake of Man's heart attack, Ken must battle Sophie - who has persuaded Man to transfer his grand master title to her in the event of his death - for the rightful claim to the familys gambling business in a riveting game of mahjong.

programme.title: Chasing the Dragon
programme.desc: Infamous real-life drug kingpin Crippled Ho came to Hong Kong as an illegal immigrant in 1963 and ruthlessly built an empire from the chaotic underworld of drug dealers and corrupt police who ruled the city under notorious detective Lee Rock.

programme.title: The Mermaid
programme.desc: A real estate tycoon plans to turn a marine protected area into a new property development, thereby destroying the secret habitat of the mermaids. A beautiful mermaid, Shan, is tasked to seduce the tycoon and stop the destruction. However, when Shans mission fails, a final, fatal war between humans and mermaids becomes inevitable.

programme.title: Endgame
programme.desc: A killer and a stage actor accidentally swapped their identities at a bathhouse. The actor must complete the killers mission while the killer thinks he is a hopeless actor after losing his memory during the accident. When the killer strives to become a successful stage actor, he also starts to recall what has happened

programme.title: Vanguard
programme.desc: A businessman Qin Guo Li is being kidnapped in London and his daughter is also in danger. The international security team, Vanguard, is hired to rescue them. Tang Huan Ting, the founder, gathers an elite team to track them down across countries, from London to Africa and Dubai. In the process, they also discover another dangerous conspiracy.

programme.title: Kung Fu Mahjong 2
programme.desc: Fanny appears to be an ordinary housewife but is in fact a mahjong expert. Deeply in love with her husband, she loses to a seductive woman, Curvy, both on the mahjong table and in competing for her husbands love. With the help from her mahjong master, Fanny vows to take on Curvy in the Mahjong King tournament!

programme.title: Stand Up Story
programme.desc: Mancer knows his father Wah is intellectually challenged since young and has to take care of him after his mother left them. When Mancer discovers and finds solace in stand-up comedy, he learns that hardships provide the best comedic material - from his own school ridicule experience to pandemic woes, misery can fuel laughter!

programme.title: Schemes in Antiques
programme.desc: Despite his familys expertise in ancient Chinese relics, Xu Yuan becomes an electronics shop owner to distance himself from his disgraced family. However, when an antique is to be returned to China, Xu Yuan uncovers an ancient mystery and soon embarks on a journey that can finally restore his familys reputation but may also cost him his life.

programme.title: First Love the Litter on the Breeze
programme.desc: This movie is the directorial debut of actor Eric Kot for Wong Kar Wai. Eric features the topic of first love in his first movie: a sleepwalker guided through the night by a lonely admirer is bizarre yet romantic, while a married grocer facing the vengeful first love that he once rejected is heartbreaking.

programme.title: Maoshan Heavenly Master
programme.desc: Prisoner Chi flees away under Master Zhangs custody, causing the latter to be expelled from his clan. On his way to find Chi, Master Zhang arrives at a place where many people vanish for no reason. He soon discovers that it is Chi who captures them in his training to become a serpent demon. The war between human and demon has just begun!

programme.title: Kungfu Stuntmen
programme.desc: Hong Kong action cinema is famous for its real kung fu moves performed by a group called Kung Fu Stuntmen. This docu-film pays tribute to the generations of kung fu stuntmen, with the crew spending over two years digging archives and interviewing many talents, including the most prominent masters like Jackie Chan, Donnie Yen and Sammo Hung.

programme.title: Black Ransom
programme.desc: Mann, an accomplished police officer, has allowed his career to wane after his wife was murdered by the mafia. However, Mann is forced to return to his former glory when he is assigned to investigate a former police inspector suspected to be kidnapping mafia bosses and demanding ransoms in exchange for their lives.

programme.title: The Mermaid
programme.desc: A real estate tycoon plans to turn a marine protected area into a new property development, thereby destroying the secret habitat of the mermaids. A beautiful mermaid, Shan, is tasked to seduce the tycoon and stop the destruction. However, when Shans mission fails, a final, fatal war between humans and mermaids becomes inevitable.

programme.title: Infernal Affairs II
programme.desc: In this prequel, the secrets of Infernal Affairs are revealed - the resentment between police superintendent Wong and crime boss Sam, as well as the beginning of the parallel fates of the two moles, Yan and Ming. The keys lie in the hands of Sam's wife, a ruthless kingpin and a righteous cop.

programme.title: Ready O/R Rot
programme.desc: Guy and Heidi are finally getting married but pressure from Guys mother creates much friction between them. Meanwhile, Grey Bear suspects his wife of cheating on him and Ken faces the biggest crisis of his life when Jessica accidentally gets pregnant. Can they eventually solve their relationship problems?

programme.title: The Lost Bladesman
programme.desc: An epic historic adventure set during the turbulent times of the Three Kingdoms. Cao Cao attempts to enlist Guan Yu into his forces, but Guan is loyal to his sworn brother Liu Bei, who is also Caos enemy. As Guan tries to rescue Liu Beis concubine from Cao, he is forced to fight his way through. Can he succeed in the end?

programme.title: The Silent War
programme.desc: After the Chinese Civil War, 701 Bureau continues to monitor the coded transmissions between rebel forces. When radio frequencies used by the opponent disappear suddenly, Agent Zhang asks Ho, a blind piano tuner with exceptional hearing, to help find the transmission signals. Can Ho find the missing signals and foil a possible assassination plot?

programme.title: Where The Wind Blows
programme.desc: Founded in the 70s, Hong Kongs ICAC is committed to fight corruption in the police force. Detectives Lui Lok and Nam Kong build a corruption system that creates conflicts between the triad and the police. When ICAC hunts down the two, their control finally comes to an end. Where the wind blows, Hong Kong is no longer what it used to be!

programme.title: I Fine… Thank You… Love You
programme.desc: Pleng, an English tutor, helps her student to pass a break up message in English to her boyfriend Gym. Gym knows nothing about English but wants to win back his girlfriend from the US, so he asks Pleng to teach him. Boorish and a slow learner, Gym makes many hilarious mistakes when learning English and ends up falling for Pleng.

programme.title: Break Up Club
programme.desc: Joe is a 20-something slacker who only takes one thing seriously: his on-and-off girlfriend Flora. After their latest breakup, Joe goes to an audition for a documentary by director Barbara Wong. Handed a camera, Joe records his discovery of a magical website that reunites him with Flora at the price of breaking up his best friend and his girlfriend. However, despite the efficiency of the website, Joe's refusal to change his immature ways and Flora's attraction to a talented graffiti artist threatens to break them up once more.

programme.title: Echoes of the Rainbow
programme.desc: Set in Hong Kong in the 1960s, the story revolves around the family of a hardworking shoemaker Mr Law, with his happy-go-lucky wife and two sons a talented elder son and an eight-year-old eccentric younger son. While their lives are not always smooth-sailing, the family sticks together and support one another through thick and thin.

programme.title: Young and Dangerous: Reloaded
programme.desc: In this remake of Young and Dangerous, Chan Ho Nam and his three buddies of the Hung Hing triad gang strive to fight for their own justice, further expanding their power in the triad and becoming a new legend...

programme.title: Flirting Scholar from the Future
programme.desc: Tiger, Lambert and Skinny Pig are massive fans of the movie, Flirting Scholar. One day, Skinny Pig who is an obscure inventor, puts together a movie time machine and accidentally sucks all of them into the movie of Flirting Scholar. The trio head off to Wah mansion to meet the maid Autumn can they find her and can they return to the present?

programme.title: S Storm
programme.desc: ICAC Chief Officer Luk witnesses a suspects murder while investigating an illegal soccer gambling case, but is unable to disclose information to Chief Inspector Lau due to his code of confidentiality, thereby hindering Laus investigation. While starting the case with mutual distrust, they end up reaching a rapport to uproot the crime syndicate.

programme.title: The Rescue
programme.desc: An emergency occurs on an offshore drilling rig that would cause it to capsize and sink. The Emergency Response Unit races against the clock in a chopper rescue mission amidst dangerous explosions and fire. Captain Gao Qian must work seamlessly with his chopper pilot Zhao Cheng to rescue survivors using the most maverick and dangerous tactics.

programme.title: Fallen Angels
programme.desc: The funkier cousin to Chungking Express, director Wong Kar Wai looks at five fallen angels who suffer love and loss amidst the crime and chaos of Hong Kongs neon nights in this movie. Karen Mok won Best Supporting Actress in the 15th Hong Kong Film Awards for her remarkable role as a broken-hearted party girl.

programme.title: See You Tomorrow
programme.desc: In this chaotic world, every city has its own "navigators" who can help solve various relationship issues. Bar owner Chen and his partner Guan are legendary navigators, but in the process of helping a girl Xiao Yu, they must also face their own problems in an epic act of self-discovery that brings their lives from towering highs to withering lows.

programme.title: Article 20
programme.desc: Han Ming, a prosecutor, faces a whirlwind of complications in his work and family lives: his son's clash with another student in school and his wife's intervention, as well as the strained partnerships at work. Amidst it all, a critical case challenges his sense of righteousness, and he decides to gamble everything to seek fairness and justice.

programme.title: The Human Goddess
programme.desc: This is a love story between an alluring fairy, Seventh Sister, who comes down from heaven to experience life in 70s Hong Kong, and a man who is running a debt laden orphanage. A heartless tycoon plans to take over the orphanage for its land but has to deal with Seventh Sisters magical powers as she aims to protect it from falling into his hands!

programme.title: Lady With A Sword
programme.desc: Swordswoman Feng tries to find a group of villains responsible for her eldest sister's death, but is shocked to discover that her fianc, Jin, is one of them. At the same time, Jin's mother and the two other killers are planning to kill Feng. Can Feng fight back and take her revenge?

programme.title: The Snake Prince
programme.desc: The Snake Prince lives on the Snake Mountain of Kwangsi with other snakes and they have lived peacefully with humans for a thousand years. All things change however, when the Snake Prince falls in love with one of the three beauties performing a sensual rain dance in the nearby village one day, and decides to marry her at all costs...

programme.title: Disco Bumpkins
programme.desc: This musical comedy is about how a young man Fen, along with his buddy Hamburger, finds love and success in the advertising world.

programme.title: The Happy Trio
programme.desc: Ah Chiao, a village girl stranded in the city, befriends a kind-hearted tramp and a retired actor. They are poor but happy, though Ah Chiaos fortune change for the better when she becomes a singer. However, she soon learns that money cannot buy one happiness...

programme.title: The Merry Wife
programme.desc: A 17-year old schoolgirl marries her 35-year-old teacher. Comedy ensues when they attempt to keep their relationship a secret despite being in the same school. When they discover unwanted suitors going after their other halves, jealousy threatens to expose their marriage any minute!

programme.title: Fast Fingers
programme.desc: After his release from prison, Uncle Bill returns to make a fortune with his past thieving partners. They continue to prey on the unsuspecting public, but are closely watched by the upright police chief, who happens to be the boyfriend of one of Uncle Bills nieces!

programme.title: The 82 Tenants
programme.desc: Continuing the success of the classic comedy House of 72 tenants, this sequel tells the stories of tenants living in an old building in Hong Kong who are forced to evict by the developers. Some tenants prefer to take the compensation while some resist the move. Will the acquisitions plan destroy the harmony of the neighborhood?

programme.title: Operation Lipstick
programme.desc: A professors assistant stole a micro-film storing the secret of a newly invented nuclear reactor and sells it to a crime syndicate. However, the micro-film accidentally falls into the hands of a nightclub dancer and a thief in the process, leading to them being relentlessly pursued by the crime syndicate to retrieve the micro-film.

programme.title: Sons Of Good Earth
programme.desc: This is an epic tale set during the time of the Sino-Japanese war. A painter Yu saves a young girl, Lotus, who is being sold to a brothel. They fall in love, get married and settled in to a peaceful life. However, their life is soon shattered by the Japanese invasion and the brutal regime that follows.

programme.title: Brothers Five
programme.desc: The five Kao brothers, separated since birth, are unaware that the master of Teng Lung Manor has killed their father. All five however, vow to defeat the vicious gangsters at the manor due to their bullying ways. After reuniting and with much discipline and hard work, the Kaos are prepared to face Lung and his gang.

programme.title: The Vengeful Beauty
programme.desc: The Flying Guillotine assassins are secretly working for the Emperor and its leader Jin is sent to kill Hon, who knows this secret. Hons pregnant wife Rong seeks to kill Jin but retreats to protect her unborn child. When she is hunted down herself, Rong hooks up with a former Flying Guillotine member and her martial arts senior to fight back...

programme.title: Dirty Ho
programme.desc: Master Wang, who is actually the 11th prince, poses as an antique connoisseur to hide his true identity. When he meets Dirty Ho, a witty con artist, Wang knows he has found the right man to help him untangle a royal succession plot...

programme.title: The Silver Fox
programme.desc: The formidable swordswoman Silver Fox was a child when her father was senselessly wounded by his step brother, and her mother raped. It is payback time eighteen years later, as her father trains her up with kung fu to take revenge on his behalf.

programme.title: Twin Blades Of Doom
programme.desc: A retired martial artist is forced to return with a vengeance after his family and friends are murdered by the evil Ghost Gang. He decides to challenge the gangs leader to a deadly duel so as to take revenge. Can he defeat the ruthless leader in the end?

programme.title: The Golden Seal
programme.desc: Dai Tian Chou practices martial arts since young so he can avenge his fathers death. He meets Wu Xiao Yan who is disguised as a man one day and is suddenly beaten by a group of gangsters. Wu begs her father to allow her to take Dai back home to recover. Little does Dai know this is his chance to take revenge.

programme.title: Shaolin Mantis
programme.desc: The Emperor orders Feng to find proofs of Master Tians rebellion in his house. Feng falls in love with Tians granddaughter and marries her. When he finds the proofs and tries to leave with her, his wife is killed in the fight against Tian. Feng creates the mantis-style martial arts and vows to avenge her death.

programme.title: Temple Of The Red Lotus
programme.desc: A young guy Wu, heads off to the Dragon Valley to meet his childhood friend Lian Chu, who was promised to be his bride. When he arrives, he finds out that the family of his bride may not be an entirely honest bunch of people. Wu wishes to take Lian Chu with him, so he has no choice but to fight against her family

programme.title: Hong Kong 73
programme.desc: In 1973, the Hong Kong Heng Seng Index hit extraordinary peaks and people from all walks of life go stock market crazy. Meanwhile, Hong Kong's social problems build up without anyone paying attention to what are actually happening to the crazy lives of people, in this mad city that many call home...

programme.title: Death Valley
programme.desc: When Jianying discovers the Zhao clan's fortune will be left to his brother Yulong, he engineers his parents' death and sends his own son out to kill Yulong.

programme.title: The Adulteress
programme.desc: The film is about the drugged, then disgraced wife of a peddler in the waning days of the Ching Dynasty. To make matters worse, shes soon framed for her husbands murder by her rapist, the son of the local magistrate! And even that is not the end of her woes in this emotional suspense

programme.title: The Battle Wizard
programme.desc: Dali Prince Tuan Yu knows nothing about martial arts, but leaves the palace for the martial arts world. He meets a snake sorceress and his mysterious half-sister. Through various misadventures, Tuan Yu gains invincible power by sucking the cobras blood and swallowing the magic toad, eventually defeating his fathers old rival.

programme.title: The Butterfly Chalice
programme.desc: Starring the stunning, teenage heartthrob Pat Ting Hung, The Butterfly Chalice marks the important directing debut of the kung-fu film genre's most principle figure Chang Cheh, as he burst the martial arts and swordplay movie doors wide open, announcing the beginning of the end for the Cantonese musicals.

programme.title: The Fighting Fool
programme.desc: Famous Kung Fu Pole master Red Eagle, is kidnapped by a villain one day. His disciple Meng, vows to rescue him. On his way, Meng encounters a greedy but great martial artist who agrees to join him in the rescue. Even though the two have extremely different personalities, they manage to team up and fight the villain in a final showdown.

programme.title: Godfather of Canton
programme.desc: A docker, Lin Si Hai, accidentally saves Commissioner Cheng who then offers him a position in the police force. Lin is smart and soon rises through the ranks through treachery and corruption, before becoming a gangster.

programme.title: The Dragon Missile
programme.desc: Sima works for a corrupt lord Qin who is suffering from a deadly disease that only a special herb can cure. Qin sends him on an urgent mission to retrieve it, but the task is made more difficult when Sima has to fight off other martial artists who want to steal the cure away from him. He has to fight with his ultimate weapon, the Dragon Missile!

programme.title: The Bride Napping
programme.desc: A rich girl Yue Ying, together with her maid Chun Lan, encounter a poor scholar Bian Ji at a fte. Chun Lan realizes Yue Ying is in love with him, but mixes his identity with a bandit due to an old servants confusion, threatening the couples union. After a series of complications, misunderstandings and mismatches, Chun Lan finally saves the day.

programme.title: Three Sinners
programme.desc: Based on the classic Ming Dynasty novel The Water Margin, Three Sinners is a Huangmei Opera about love, betrayal, murder, and redemption. Starring Hong Kong's premiere movie couple, it is one of the grandest Eastmancolor-Shawscope costume musicals in the Shaw Brothers library.

programme.title: Heaven Sword and Dragon Sabre
programme.desc: In the Yuan Dynasty, martial artists everywhere battle for the Heaven Sword and the Dragon Sabre, as only when these two powerful weapons combine can a secret be revealed to help one become the king of the martial arts world. As Zhang Wu Ji acquires the skills from Nine Yang Scriptures by chance, he is also embroiled in this lengthy battle.

programme.title: The Singing Escort
programme.desc: Betty Ting plays Susan, a young woman hiding from her father by being a nightclub singer in Japan. Pop singer Chao Ke-jen (Lin Chong) gets permission from his boss to visit Japan, with the condition that he finds the boss's daughter. Boy finds girl, boy falls in love. But will the father approve?

programme.title: Buddha's Palm
programme.desc: Young Long Jian Fei, a martial arts novice, is adopted by the Fire Spirit Demon who taught him the powerful Buddha's Palm, turning Long into a martial arts master. Long is tasked by the Fire Spirit Demon to takes revenge for his master, and this soon unleashes a storm upon the martial arts world

programme.title: Roving Swordsman
programme.desc: An ambitious evil clan intends to rule the martial arts world. To achieve their goal, they must first steal a secret martial arts manuscript depicting how firearms can be produced. However, a supremely intelligent swordsman Shen Sheng Yi is protecting the manuscript and remains one step ahead of the evil clan.

programme.title: Dragon Swamp
programme.desc: Fan is cheated by her lover Tong to steal her masters Jade Dragon Sword. She is jailed in the Dragon Swamp as punishment and gave birth to a pair of twins - her daughter is raised by her master, while her son is taken by Tong. Twenty years later, the sword is stolen again and Fans daughter goes seeking for it, meeting Fans friend along the way.

programme.title: Big Times for the Crazy Bumpkins
programme.desc: Ah Niu finds a bag of jewels on the street and becomes rich. It is at this time that Uncle Zhou asks him to sign a contract to marry a girl, but it turns out to be a trap for Ah Niu to sell his house. In the end, Ah Niu becomes poor again

programme.title: The Daredevils
programme.desc: Corrupt general Wang Li assumes power by killing his superior. The son of the murdered superior befriends four street performers called The Venoms, and they help him take revenge by posing as government officials offering a peace token to the corrupt general. When Wang arrives at a warehouse, he is ambushed by the Venoms!

programme.title: The Purple Shell
programme.desc: Hui and Ha are stuck in their unhappy marriages and are attracted to each other when they meet at a party. In one of their beach strolls, Ha picks up a purple shell and gives it to Hui as a memento. When Huis husband finds out about them, he hurts Hui and causes her to become seriously ill, while also blackmails Ha. How will this love story end?

programme.desc: The Great Elephant Tale - Follow the adventures of three elephants across three very distinct African habitats. Their travels combine to tell the story of how these emotional and intelligent creatures evolved over millions of years to survive on the continent.

programme.desc: Careful, There's Humans Up There! - Follow the southern team as they test new migration tech and tools that could reduce shark attacks in a popular snorkelling spot. Then catch and tag bull sharks with the northern team, who want to help local swimmers steer clear of birthing mothers.

programme.title: Super Shark Highway S1 Ep2
programme.desc: Love Bites - Track a pregnant shark along the Great Barrier Reef and see if she leads a team of scientists to her hidden pupping ground. Then search for signs of mating along the southern coast that could reveal a very shy female megashark in search of a partner.

programme.title: Super Shark Highway S1 Ep3
programme.desc: Into the Darkness - Stay up late as the northern team attaches an activity tag to a bull shark and finds out what this night owl does after sunset. Then dive 80 meters deep with the southern team, who are hoping to put a satellite tracker on a female great white.

programme.title: Super Shark Highway S1 Ep4
programme.desc: The Social Network - Ponder shark community hierarchies as the northern team studies how young blacktips learn social and survival skills. Then rush to Rainbow Beach with the southern team, who are eager to witness the sand tiger sharks most elusive behaviour: mating.

programme.title: Super Shark Highway S1 Ep5
programme.desc: Detour - Travel to the ends of Australias shark highways. Find out if Greenly Island in the south is a truck stop for migrating great whites, then search for proof of a genetic connection between northern bull sharks and their cooler-climate cousins.

programme.title: Super Shark Highway S1 Ep6
programme.desc: Careful, There's Humans Up There! - Follow the southern team as they test new migration tech and tools that could reduce shark attacks in a popular snorkelling spot. programme.title: Wild Castles S1 Ep1
programme.desc: Heidelberg - Explore beautiful Heidelberg Castle whose ruins stand in imposing wonder beside the river Neckar in Western Germany. Surrounded by a protected nature reserve, the castle is home to birds of prey and acts as a spawning ground for nearby amphibians.

programme.title: Life's Journey S1 Ep2
programme.desc: Life's Lessons - If young animals survive until adulthood, the chances for survival are greatly increased - but many challenges face them before they can strike out on their own. Some have months to grow-up; other have decades but all, have lots to learn along the way.

programme.title: Wildlife ER S3 Ep1

programme.title: Wildlife ER S3 Ep2
programme.desc: A Prickly Problem - Join vets Emily and Martine in the OR, where Dolly the koalas spaying surgery takes a scary turn. Aid a run-over echidna with vet Nigel, see rescue officer Chantelles slick fix for a snared lizard, and probe a possible birdnapping with vet Karina.

programme.title: My Best Friend's An Animal S1 Ep2
programme.desc: Bandit, Max, and George - Learn how cockatoos and platypuses inspired new careers, then explore the shared trauma that bonded a human and an elephant for life. Get playful with 35-year-old George the turkey vulture and say a moving farewell to human-raised kangaroos.

programme.title: Orangutan Jungle School S2 Ep3
programme.desc: Kesi Turns a Corner - Watch a milestone moment when two students get their first forest time in years. And another pair of students are confined to the schools clinic after an accident in the forest leaves Beni with a broken leg and Lala with a broken elbow.

programme.title: Orangutan Jungle School S2 Ep4
programme.desc: Bears on the Move - Beni and Lala are going stir crazy in the sick bay, but they must recover before returning to the rough and tumble of class. And at forest school, a termite-foraging lesson inspires class clown Valentino to make a finger-licking discovery.

programme.title: Orangutan Jungle School S2 Ep5
programme.desc: Wines New Friend - Join two seriously ill orangutans in the medical clinic, where Eriks head infection is causing concern and fourteen-year-old Mias life depends on a blood transfusion. Outside the clinic, the infants find a secret treat hidden inside a rubber tree.

programme.title: Orangutan Jungle School S2 Ep6
programme.desc: Bald is Beautiful - After a terrible accident at the nursery forest school, life changes drastically for nine-month-old Alejandra. And at forest school, the students enjoy a poolside classroom where Valentino proves hes much more than just a class clown.

programme.title: Orangutan Jungle School S2 Ep7
programme.desc: The Road to Recovery - Beni and Lala get an unexpected visit from Vet Arga, Kesi makes a new friend on Bangamat Island, and Alejandra deals with a new view of the world after the accident at forest school leaves her blind in one eye.

programme.title: Wild Castles S1 Ep2

programme.title: Island of the Monsoon S1 Ep4
programme.desc: Web of Life - A manmade lake in Minneriya National Park supports the largest concentration of elephants in Asia. Follow a young male who has reached a turning point toward adulthood. In the rainforest, jungles teem with a variety of bizarre species of insects.

programme.title: Island of the Monsoon S1 Ep5

programme.title: Island of the Monsoon S1 Ep6
programme.desc: Life on the Wing - Yala National Park is an avian Eden, home to 215 species of bird. This paradise offers many possibilities for parents who can weather the ever-changing climate. Every species must either raise their offspring here or find a new home before the dry season

He sets out to prove Creek is a liar./ Branch presents Trolls Village with a time capsule which will survive the ages. The Trolls are excited by the prospect of making friends with future Trolls. programme.title: Trolls: The Beat Goes On! Ep52

programme.title: All Hail King Julien Ep51
